data.description: Welcome to this stunning 2-bedroom condo that has undergone a complete transformation, featuring solar panels! It features an open concept layout that's perfect for hosting guests. As you enter, you'll be greeted by the warm, new floors that extend throughout the space, creating an inviting atmosphere. The newly installed lighting fixtures elegantly illuminate every corner, enhancing the overall aesthetic. The open kitchen connects with the dining room, and has been remodeled to perfection with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample storage for all your needs. The bathroom has been thoughtfully updated, featuring sleek modern finishes. This condo offers versatility for various living arrangements, with two generously sized bedrooms.    The home is conveniently situated within a 5-10 minute radius of various amenities, including schools, making it an ideal location for military personnel. Additionally, there's a playground and a pool located behind the house. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this updated 2-bedroom condo your new home! This condo is VA APPROVED!! Contact us today to schedule a viewing!
